The iron dart tip is a dart tip made with the Smithing skill. Players can craft this item using an iron bar on an anvil with a hammer in their inventory and a Smithing level of 19. Each iron bar creates 10 iron dart tips and gives the player 25 Smithing experience. They can be fletched into iron darts at level 22 Fletching when used with feathers, granting 38 Fletching experience per 10 darts made.

To smith darts, one must complete the Tourist Trap quest.
